      <title>普京要求我们特使在谈话后向特朗普传达信息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/moscow-targeted-in-drone-attack-after-us-envoy-s-visit-to-putin</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克里姆林宫说，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）要求在与莫斯科的美国特使史蒂夫·维特科夫（Steve Witkoff）进行深夜对话中，向美国唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）传达信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/moscow-targeted-in-drone-attack-after-us-envoy-s-visit-to-putin</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 08:13:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国和俄罗斯在伊朗的背后团结了特朗普计划的挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/iran-china-call-to-end-curbs-after-tehran-spurned-trump-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国和俄罗斯加入伊朗谴责美国制裁，并支持恢复与德黑兰一项具有里程碑意义的核协议的努力，唐纳德·特朗普总统在他的第一任期内放弃了，现在想取代。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/iran-china-call-to-end-curbs-after-tehran-spurned-trump-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 06:04:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非在异议中权衡预算变化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/south-african-budget-changes-in-play-as-parties-reject-tax-hikes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非财政部长伊诺克·戈格瓦纳（Enoch Godongwana）可能必须对国家预算进行更改，因为当事方控制了一半以上的议会席位，拒绝了他提高税收的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/south-african-budget-changes-in-play-as-parties-reject-tax-hikes</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 12:55:42 GMT</pubDate>
